uws.job.user

Class DefaultJobOwner

  • java.lang.Object
    • uws.job.user.DefaultJobOwner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JobOwner

    public final class DefaultJobOwner
extends java.lang.Object
implements JobOwner

    Default implementation of JobOwner.

    In this implementation, a job owner has only an ID and a pseudo (which may be the same). However, other informations may be added thanks to putUserData(String, String). These additional data will also be saved with the ID and the pseudo/name of the user by a backup manager.

    Version:
    05/2012
    Author:
    Grégory Mantelet (CDS)
